<h3>Amendments and Updates</h3>
<p>Adding shareholders, changing business activities, increasing share capital, or modifying governance provisions all require certified translation of the amendments. We can translate consolidated MOAs showing all changes, or individual amendment documents as required by the receiving authority. For complex corporate histories with multiple amendments, we recommend a comprehensive approach to ensure consistency.</p>

<blockquote class="hero-pullquote">If any UAE bank or authority rejects our MOA translation due to our error, we correct and redeliver at no charge—including courier costs for urgent bank appointments.</blockquote>

